title.rendered: Channing Tatum Posts Buck A$$ Nude Photo After Losing at Jenga to Jessie J

content.rendered:
Reading Time: 3 minutes

It has been six months since Channing Tatum and Jessie J went public.

They’re still together, and it looks like they’re having a lot of fun — especially Jessie.

Because it’s thanks to her that fans all over the world can glimpse Channing’s naked body in all of it’s glory.

There are thirst traps in this world, where an arm or collarbone or midsections or upper thigh or hip bone are on display.

And then there’s this photo of the famously hunky Channing Tatum.

This pic shows off everything that he can’t cover with his hands, because the only thing that he’s "wearing" is water droplets.

This artistic nude of Channing in ther shower was not stolen from his phone by some vicious hacker, so don’t worry.

Instead, it was uploaded by the studly star himself — after he lost a wager.

In the captions, Channing explains why the tantalizing photo is now available for public enjoyment.

He writes that he "lost a game of Jenga to Jessica Cornish."

"The loser (me) had to post a picture the other person (Jessica Cornish) picked…" he details.

"Smh and fml…" Channing adds, meaning "smacking my head" and "f–k my life."

He vows: "I’m never playing Jenga with her ever again…"

Girlfriend Jessie was the culprit behind Channing’s extremely public nudity.

Since she selected the image, she obviously wasn’t too miffed that the whole world was eyeing her slice of beefcake.

In fact, she left an encouraging comment under Channing’s Instagram post.

"Sharing is caring," Jessie writes.

Anyone else get the impression that she chose this picture so that she could brag about what she’s tapping?

That’s the vibe that we’re getting, anyway.

If you’re very pleased with Jessie’s choice, you’re not alone.

Fans and even celebrity friends poured into the comments to heap praise upon the photo.

"She just became mad people’s hero," one comment reads.

"The response to this, I predict, is gonna be biblical," states another.

"No no, you keep playing Jenga," implores another fan. "Sincerely, everyone."

Real talk?

One, Channing Tatum knows that he’s hot. He’s been high on people’s celebrity crush lists for a solid decade, now.

Two, before he was a movie star, he was a stripper — so he’s familiar with being seen wearing very little, if not usually by so many people.

We accused Jessie of choosing this photo so that she can brag about the hotness of the guy she’s banging.

But we have to consider that maybe Channing sharing it is a form of humblebrag.

After all, he’s the hottie getting thirsted after by a bajillion people. Maybe he’s not feeling as bashful as the caption suggests.

Channing and Jessie J went public with their romance in October of last year.

It was around that time that Channing’s ex, actress and dancer Jenna Dewan, officially filed for divorce.

Six months earlier, in April of 2018, Jenna and Channing had announced their separation after nine years of marriage.

A lot of fans of the two were heartbroken, both on their behalf but also because they were fans of them as a couple, specifically.

But it looks like they’re both moving on and finding new happiness. Sometimes, that’s how life works out.
